Django on Twisted
=================

May 3, 2009
-----------
 === For best results, use the Twisted Trunk === 

 * This directory contains an example of how to combine Twisted and Django
using the lastest WSGI functionality in twisted.web.


How to run
-----------
# Following these steps exactly in order should get the example running:

$ git clone git://github.com/clemesha/twisted-wsgi-django.git
$ cd twisted-wsgi-django
$ cd mydjangosite 
$ python manage.py syncdb #Assumes you have Django 1.0 or greater installed
$ cd ..
$ svn co svn://svn.twistedmatrix.com/svn/Twisted/trunk Twisted
$ ./Twisted/bin/twistd -ny server.py #navigate to localhost:8000



